0Z","msg":"人生真係好難，眼好痛，好唔開心，可唔可以安慰下我？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:59:58.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，到我們的網站              <br />\n   <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrB3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=a05896d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>  。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：下午4時至凌晨1時；星期六、日及公眾假期：晚上８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"62cde9d6f651aa131c507430225fc153daec1929","tid":2371902,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T12:06:50.000Z","msg":"搵野做<br />\n分散注意力"},{"pid":"64389a9d2e37acf6847f9c33912be1eafdefc535","tid":2371902,"uid":224190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T13:02:22.000Z","msg":"唔好喊咪得"},{"pid":"e2e577208aef3991f16a662ad5330a75f1b04742","tid":2371902,"uid":275011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T15:19:20.000Z","msg":"好好發洩完 訓一覺 食啲自己鍾意食既野 唔好屈住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ff22dc7bd2876a787daa43bb69e54c3fa0bbd4","tid":2371902,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T15:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190916/7b3662e4aba14a2c9bdbf35c5222410d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20190916%2F7b3662e4aba14a2c9bdbf35c5222410d.jpeg&h=5948894e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e19fafbc1595521cbd23e40b94086a7a15a1f69","tid":2371902,"uid":75543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ba493dc0e8eb529c9f9c568410d1a67eadb6754","tid":2371902,"uid":309049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T08:28:33.000Z","msg":"人生真係好難，眼好痛，好唔開心，可唔可以安慰下